description: The Super Young Team are real heroes! And if you don't believe them please check out the Mission Statement on their website. Or peruse the video log of their charity work that's posted on several social networking sites. And while you're at it, go ahead and check out the fabulous new t-shirt designs in their web store. All-new t-shirts are 110% bio-friendly; meaning that they actually leave the environment better than it was before you bought the shirt. Can the JLA say that about their merchandise?

description:
The new-reader-friendly direction of Gold Digger continues!

Gina's class is assigned to investigate Mynos Siegeweld—by mistake, as Gina's misfiled their assignment papers with her recent, dangerous research! Now Elroy Nabbum, Aljabra Gihom, Anton Fyst, and the semi-captive love goddess Venus find themselves on the site of an ancient, deadly battle—a battle still going on in the mind of its one vengeful survivor!
name: Rainbow Dark

description: Eisner-nominated artist Chuck BB (BLACK METAL) joins the WASTELAND crew for a special standalone issue! The story of how Marcus founded Newbegin is known to everyone in the city. But how is it told... and just how true is it? Join the audience and gather round, as Newbegin's famous marketplace storyteller is about to begin the tale!
name: Apocalyptic City
The Battle of the Berserk Machines

description: Continued from GEN13 ANNUAL '99, "Slipstream" concludes as the members of GEN13 and DV8 combine forces in a last-ditch effort to thwart the schemes of one of WildStorm's oldest villains! But even if they succeed, they'll still have to face off against each other - and it's a battle that one of the players won't survive! Shocks and guest-stars abound in the wrap-up to the story fans have been waiting for! This special giant-sized issue also contains a backup story with art by former DV8 artist Juvaun Kirby!
name: Slipstream Part. 3, Second Time Around

description: Two unassuming auto repair shop owners discover that monsters are infesting the world. When they are attacked, the glowing blue juice from the monster's brain heals his arm and saves Jake's life. But this gift only begins a life-long link to the monster invasion. From the creators of Sci-Fi TV's Lost Room mini-series.
name: Chapter One
Big Boy and the Bully of Baker Street

description: Alex Elder is angry and confused. He is adapting to his new vampire condition, discovering that he possesses powers beyond his imagination. Now he is ready to explore a new world hiding in the shadows--and to take on the guys responsible for his death, the "Jelly-Bats" gang, only this time things have changed!
name: Unlife Story

description: The battle is on! At last, Alex Elder comes face to face with his killer--ROSE, the evil leader of the Jelly-Bats. He's all alone and the odds are stacked heavily against him. Will he be able to survive this final test and, in so doing, confront himself and the creature he has become?
name: Payment in Blood

description:
She¹s sexy, she¹s lethal, she¹s French, and no wolf would ever dream of messing with her. She¹s the Red Hood--a demon hunter who¹s out for blood!

Humberto Ramos¹ foray into the dark world of a young vampire continues as we meet the most dangerous beauty in the Big Apple--and discover that she¹s trying to uncover a conspiracy involving Alex...and his family
name: The Children of Judas, Part One: Politics in the Blood

description: Alex is looking for answers. He must find the Red Hood to know why she attacked his father. Meanwhile, the Children of Judas, a bunch of wild kids you wouldn't like to meet, are ready to get rid of the vampire hunters once and for all. Can Alex and the Red Hood stop the kids without getting killed? Maybe--if they don't kill each other first!
name: The Children of Judas, Part Two: Behind the Hood

description:
It's the year 2200, and Homer J. Simpson XIII is the curator of a museum dedicated to the exploits of history's most famous family of the 21st century.

Take a guided tour with us as we reveal all the times the Simpson family saved the world - whether they planned to or not!
name: The Simpsons Save The World

description: When Springfield is named the Ugliest City in America, citing Selma and Patty as prime examples of the city's populace, Marge takes matters into her own hands. Chances are things are going to get a lot uglier before they get, um, less ugly!
name: Marge's Extreme Make-Under

description: Crimson revolves around a young man named Alex Elder who is attacked by a gang of vampires while out late with his friends. Bitten, Alex is saved by Ekimus, the last of an ancient race pre-dating humanity, who claims Alex is the chosen one. Alex becomes the first and last of his kind, gaining powers beyond that of a normal vampire. As the chosen one, he will bring the end to vampirekind.
